name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Collector: Export any page to excel

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Collector detects any structure within a webpage and allows you to export it to excel.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Collector is a single click solution for all your web scraping needs. It detects any structure within a webpage and allows you to export it to excel. With privacy in mind, no browsing data on any of the html pages you've visited will be sent to the server.
